verbose_text: In group D, the RA level in the eyes of guinea pigs with LIM decreased from 12.18 +/-01.23 ng/100 mg to 2.55 +/-0.18 ng/100 mg on the 14th day after the injection of LE540, which was significantly lower than the level observed in the normal control eyes or contralateral eyes at the same time point.
